title: 'the trick: symlinkJoin'
pid: 4a863b21-1878-47b5-a3f6-eed3a7f7579e
body: |2-
  # in packages.nix:
  #+BEGIN_SRC nix
  { pkgs, ... }:

  {
    environment.systemPackages =
      with pkgs; [
        ...
        (symlinkJoin {
          name = "jbb-plugins";
          paths = [
            drumgizmo
  	        ...
            ] } ) ] }
  #+END_SRC
